## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the Industrial Revolution's impact. The sources used are primarily educational and may lack the depth of peer-reviewed academic research. Additionally, the focus is on broad impacts, and specific regional or sectoral effects may not be fully addressed. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the nuanced ways in which the Industrial Revolution continues to influence modern society.